A stall owner who is selling his flowers to female customers looks very enthusiastic.
"Take a look and take a look! Oh, this lady really has good eyesight, my apricot blossom is not only as beautiful as you, but also has a fragrance. Put it on your body, even the wine in the store is three points more fragrant. "

chinese.name: 卖花摊主
chinese.description:
一位正在向女顾客推售自家花枝的摊主，看起来十分热情。
“瞧一瞧看一看嘞！哟，这位夫人真是好眼力，我这杏花枝不单像您一样美丽动人，还香气四溢，放在身上，连正店的酒可都多香三分。”

name: Restaurant Guest A
description:
Business in this tea shop is booming, and the shop assistants are busy cleaning up. There is an endless stream of people who come to eat here, and several guests are waiting for their refreshments to be served.
"That person is already eating, why haven't the refreshments I ordered come up yet?"

chinese.name: 食客甲
chinese.description:
这家茶肆生意正旺，店铺伙计正忙着收拾，来此处就餐的人络绎不绝，几个客人正在等待着他们的茶点端上来。
“那人都吃撑了，我点的茶点为什么还没上来？”

name: Idle Soldier A
description:
A group of soldiers on official business, but they are not mindful of their tasks, they just slouchy gathering outside the yamen, or sitting or lying down waiting for the officer to appear.
"Spring is sleepy and autumn is lacking, and summer is nap, and winter is March when I can't wake up. Every day is a good time to sleep."

chinese.name: 懒散士卒甲
chinese.description:
一群公务在身的士卒，但他们对于自己的任务并不上心，只是懒懒散散地聚在衙门外，或坐或躺地等待着长官出现。
“春困秋乏夏打盹，睡不醒的冬三月。每天都是睡觉的好时候。”

name: Tax Officer B
description:
A tax officer with a checking account book in his hand is checking all the taxes on goods brought by the coachmen.
"Yes, it is 70% written in black and white on my side. No, it is not 70% of yours, but 70% of the government. Your textiles come in from outside, and you sell them cheaply. Can you still do business in the city? Don't talk nonsense, just follow the rules."

chinese.name: 税务官乙
chinese.description:
一位手里拿着核验账本的税务官，正在把车夫们运来的货物税款一一清点明白。
“对，我这边白纸黑字写的就是七成。不，不是你们七成，是官府七成。你们这批纺织品是从外边进来的，你们便宜卖，那城里的生意还做不做了？行了别废话，就按规定来。”

name: The Palanquin-Carrier
description: A bearer who has just put down a heavy sedan chair, no matter how comfortable the people in the sedan chair are, this kind of action tool still needs manpower to carry.

chinese.name: 轿夫
chinese.description: 一位刚刚把沉重的轿子放下来的轿夫，不管在轿子里的人有多么安逸，这种行动工具终究还是需要人力来背负的。

name: The Pedestrians
description: Compared with the busyness on a narrow boat, the pedestrians on the river bank seem to be very leisurely. In that era, people who went out on horseback were generally much wealthier than those who lived on the boat. They usually had the opportunity to go to the slow and leisurely. life.

chinese.name: 行路人
chinese.description: 与窄船上的忙碌相比，河岸上的行路人倒是显得十分悠闲，在那个时代，出门骑马的人一般都要比生活在船上的人要富裕得多，他们通常有机会去过那种慢悠悠的生活。

name: Troubled Carter B
description: The two coachmen pressed forward and dragged them in an attempt to reduce the inertia of the vehicle’s sliding. The donkey’s advancing inertia made it difficult to control itself. It staggered. It turned its head to avoid the trafficker. It was dangerous. In modern terms, their car was obviously Already overweight.

chinese.name: 避险车夫乙
chinese.description: 两个车夫前压后拽，企图减轻车辆下滑的惯性，毛驴前进的惯性使它难以自控，打着趔趄，它侧首回避贩夫，可谓险象环生，用现代的话来说，他们的车显然是已经超重了。

name: Sculler-Holding Boatman A
description:
Several boatmen joined together and used their best to hold a boat scull. The characteristic of this kind of boat is that there are two huge boat sculls at the fore and aft of the ship.
"Don't rush, I haven't seen any big winds and waves, don't overturn the boat in this calm river!"

chinese.name: 掌橹船夫甲
chinese.description:
几个船夫合在一起，用尽全力掌住了一只船橹，这种船的特点就在于船的首尾有两只巨大的船橹。
“动作不要急，老子什么大风大浪没见过，可别在这风平浪静的河里翻了船！”

name: Cash-In-Transit Guard B
description: The seemingly crude wooden car in the picture is actually a money-carrying truck. Two hotel guys are carrying and counting the copper coins. Holding so much money, even if it is not your own, you should be very excited. The bundles of copper coins are very heavy. , It is very hard to hold.

chinese.name: 运钞伙计乙
chinese.description: 图中这个看似简陋的木车其实是辆运钞车，两个酒店伙计正在搬运与清点铜钱，抱着这么多钱，就算不是自己的，也应该会很激动吧，成捆的铜钱非常沉重，抱着很是费劲。

name: Boatman B
description: The water flow suddenly reversed, causing the boat to sway violently. The boatman standing on the side of the boat firmly grasped the board to prevent himself from falling into the water. It is not common for river water to invert, but every time it happens, it will bring the river to the river. The waves are so big that people can hardly guard against it.

chinese.name: 船工乙
chinese.description: 水流突然倒转，使得船剧烈晃动，站在船侧的船工紧紧地抓着船板，让自己不至于掉进水里，河水倒灌这种事情并不常见，只是每一次发生，都会给河流带来不小的波浪，让人防不胜防。

name: The Storyteller
description:
A storyteller surrounded by a group of listeners. He is very involved in his face, and occasionally uses his body movements to increase his persuasiveness, so that the audience can have an immersive experience.
"Last time the book said that the great hero was sitting in the house and he could only hear it! The sound of Xiujian. The secret in my heart is not good, and there is clearly a thief outside! Pick up the robe, take it, and walk outside, standing in the garden Look and see. A dark shadow moves from east to west. The hero presses the goose wings and retracts the spring. Cang Cang claps the treasure knife out of its sheath, making a field battle with a hidden knife in all directions."

chinese.name: 说书人
chinese.description:
一位被听客团团围住的说书人。他面上十分投入，间或用肢体动作增强说服力，使听众产生身临其境的体验。
“上回书讲到，大英雄正在屋中闷坐，只听得咻啪！袖箭声音。心中暗道不好，外面分明有了贼了！撩袍，端带，往外就走，站在园中观瞧。一道黑影由东往西，大英雄按雁翅，退绷簧。苍啷啷宝刀出鞘，使了个野战八方藏刀式。”

name: The Flower Stall Owner
description:
A stall owner who is selling his flowers to female customers looks very enthusiastic.
"Take a look and take a look! Oh, this lady really has good eyesight, my apricot blossom is not only as beautiful as you, but also has a fragrance. Put it on your body, even the wine in the store is three points more fragrant. "

chinese.name: 卖花摊主
chinese.description:
一位正在向女顾客推售自家花枝的摊主，看起来十分热情。
“瞧一瞧看一看嘞！哟，这位夫人真是好眼力，我这杏花枝不单像您一样美丽动人，还香气四溢，放在身上，连正店的酒可都多香三分。”

name: The Herb-Drinks Vendor
description: A fragrant drinker vendor introducing his own drinks to customers. You see, our drink can not only relieve heat and heat, but also dispel dampness and detoxification. It can also strengthen the body and cure all kinds of diseases. After drinking it, it is very cool, two mouthfuls, three mouthfuls, bright, four mouthfuls ...Guests, would you like to try?

chinese.name: 香饮子摊贩
chinese.description: 一位在给客人介绍自家饮品的香饮子摊贩。您看，咱家的饮子不仅能解暑消热，还能祛湿排毒，还能强身健体，还能包治百病，喝下去一口透心凉，两口心飞扬，三口心明眼亮，四口……客人您要不试试？

name: Idle Soldier D
description:
A group of soldiers on official business, but they are not mindful of their tasks, they just slouchy gathering outside the yamen, or sitting or lying down waiting for the officer to appear.
"Continue to sleep, keep on sleeping. If you don't get enough sleep, there is no strength to hurry."

chinese.name: 懒散士卒丁
chinese.description:
一群公务在身的士卒，但他们对于自己的任务并不上心，只是懒懒散散地聚在衙门外，或坐或躺地等待着长官出现。
“继续睡继续睡，不睡饱哪有力气赶路。”

name: The Exhausted Porter
description: A porter walking wearily on the street, the cargo on both ends of the pole seemed to be heavy, which made him stagger while walking while bending over to transfer the weight, until a shout made him raise his head, only to realize that the road in front of him was surrounded by a group of people. The official master blocked it.

chinese.name: 疲惫挑夫
chinese.description: 一位疲惫地行走在街上的挑夫，扁担两头的货物看似很沉重，这让他步履蹒跚着一边走一边弯腰转移重量，直到一声吆喝让他抬起头来，才发现眼前的路被一群官家老爷堵住了。

name: The Discontent Bystander
description:
Xu is the old man who praised his ointment as a magical medicine, and there was a circle of people standing around, all of them listened carefully, and even the porter on the road looked distractedly.
"If this plaster is so amazing, it would be a good thing to buy one and go back to my father."

chinese.name: 不忿看客
chinese.description:
许是这位老者把自己的药膏夸为神药，周围站了一圈人，个个听得认真，连赶路的挑夫都分神往这边张望。
“若是这膏药真有如此神妙，买一帖回去给家父也是好事。”

name: The Teenage Farmer
description: The young man who was not in his hair-cutting year led the donkey team composed of five donkeys and came to the prosperous Bianjing full of charcoal. Maybe it was for life or to sell in the city.

chinese.name: 少年农夫
chinese.description: 不及束发之年的少年，在由五只驴组成的驴队之前牵头，驼着满满当当的木炭走向繁华的汴京，也许是生活之用，也许为了到城里售卖。

name: Tax Officer C
description:
A tax officer sitting in front of the hall in the house, with a spread record in front of him, preparing to register a new tax payment into the treasury.
"This bookkeeping is also tiring work. From morning to night, you can't make any mistakes. You can't add more to the two and write it as three... It's broken, if you say that it is a sudden tax of 30%, I am afraid People will guess that I wrote it wrong. If there is, it is said that the new rules will be divided into three to seven. Seventy percent will go to the official family, let them quarrel, and they will not notice."

chinese.name: 税务官丙
chinese.description:
一位坐在屋内堂前的税务官，面前是摊开来的记录，准备将新的一笔税款登记入库。
“这记账啊，也是份累人的活。从早记到晚，还不能有误。你看这个二就不能多添一笔写成三……坏了，若说是突然收三成税，怕是会被人猜到是我写错了。有了，就说是新规三七分成。七成归官家，让他们吵去，就不会注意到了。”

name: The Laundering Old Woman
description: On the banks of the Bian River, a family boat arrived. An old woman dumped swill out of the boat. His jacket and crotchless pants were hanging on the canopy. The boat family maintained a hard drifting life on the water. This life was very hard, but it must continue.

chinese.name: 老妪
chinese.description: 汴河岸边，一条家船抵岸，一位老妪往船外倾倒泔水，船篷上晾晒着上衣和无裆裤，船家在水上维持着艰辛的漂泊生活，这样的生活很辛苦，但总得继续下去。

traits.value: Light blue color matching short sleeves

name: Bystander A
description: When the shipwreck was about to happen, the spectators at the bridge head pointed, or exclaimed, enclosing the right side guardrail of the arch bridge, and several people tried to rescue them by crossing the railings. In fact, in this case, everyone is the same. In a panic, no one can tell whether they are helping or adding chaos.

chinese.name: 看客甲
chinese.description: 船难将发之时，桥头的看客或指指点点，或惊呼不已，把拱桥的右侧护栏围得水泄不通，有几个人越过栏杆企图施救，其实，这种情况下，所有人都是慌张的，他们是在帮忙，还是在添乱，没人分得清楚。

name: Silk Store Customer B
description:
A customer who is sitting sideways on a silk paving bench seems to be comparing the details of the product.
"I said the shopkeeper, the shop is bullying. Why do you hide this fine silk so deep? It's specially left for me? People are always treacherous and slippery, so I have to look for them again."

chinese.name: 帛铺顾客乙
chinese.description:
一位侧坐在帛铺长凳上，似乎正在对比商品细节的顾客。
“我说掌柜的，店大欺客啊。怎么把这上好的绸子藏得这么深？专门给我留下的？人老奸马老滑，我可得再找找看。”

name: Bystander D
description: When the shipwreck was about to happen, the spectators at the bridge head pointed, or exclaimed, enclosing the right side guardrail of the arch bridge, and several people tried to rescue them by crossing the railings. In fact, in this case, everyone is the same. In a panic, no one can tell whether they are helping or adding chaos.

chinese.name: 看客丁
chinese.description: 船难将发之时，桥头的看客或指指点点，或惊呼不已，把拱桥的右侧护栏围得水泄不通，有几个人越过栏杆企图施救，其实，这种情况下，所有人都是慌张的，他们是在帮忙，还是在添乱，没人分得清楚。

name: Servant B
description:
At the entrance of the tea shop, a guest slowly climbed up the back of the donkey. Xu Shi had just finished eating and planned to ride the donkey home. His servants were asking him to ride the donkey.
"Master, you drank too much again, come, I will help you on the donkey."

chinese.name: 侍从乙
chinese.description:
茶肆门口有客人缓慢地往驴背上爬，许是刚吃完饭，打算骑驴回家，他的仆从们正在招呼他骑上驴。
“老爷您又喝多了，来，我扶您上驴。”

name: The Shading Scholar
description: If you are afraid of going out, you don’t have to worry about it. The round fan covers your face to relieve your sorrow. Don’t be afraid to see acquaintances. In any case, this customary rule seems to have rescued the social phobia player who does not want to greet people on the street, but they are already so close, did the face-blocking action come a little later?

chinese.name: 遮面文人
chinese.description: 社恐出门不用愁，圆扇遮面来解忧，见到熟人不必怕，举起物件挡一下。不管怎样，这种约定俗成的规则似乎确实解救了这位不愿在街上和人打招呼的社交恐惧症选手，只是都已经离得这样近了，挡脸的动作是不是来得稍晚了一些？

name: Sculler-Holding  Boatman B
description:
Several boatmen joined together and used their best to hold a boat scull. The characteristic of this kind of boat is that there are two huge boat sculls at the fore and aft of the ship.
"(I always feel that someone is trying to reverse it, otherwise the boat would not be so slow.)"

chinese.name: 掌橹船夫乙
chinese.description:
几个船夫合在一起，用尽全力掌住了一只船橹，这种船的特点就在于船的首尾有两只巨大的船橹。
“（总觉得有人使力使反了，不然船不至于这么慢。）”

name: The Herb-Drinks Vendor
description: A fragrant drinker vendor introducing his own drinks to customers. You see, our drink can not only relieve heat and heat, but also dispel dampness and detoxification. It can also strengthen the body and cure all kinds of diseases. After drinking it, it is very cool, two mouthfuls, three mouthfuls, bright, four mouthfuls ...Guests, would you like to try?

chinese.name: 香饮子摊贩
chinese.description: 一位在给客人介绍自家饮品的香饮子摊贩。您看，咱家的饮子不仅能解暑消热，还能祛湿排毒，还能强身健体，还能包治百病，喝下去一口透心凉，两口心飞扬，三口心明眼亮，四口……客人您要不试试？

name: Drinker A
description: The wine customers in front of the winery, the Northern Song Dynasty officials feared that the people would gather to drink and cause rebellion, so it was forbidden to gather to drink. Therefore, the customers of the winery were mostly individual guests in twos and threes. However, as long as there is wine and friends, there are as many as the number of people. What does it matter?

chinese.name: 酒客甲
chinese.description: 酒庄前的酒客，北宋官府怕老百姓聚众饮酒后，引起造反，所以禁止聚众饮酒，因此酒庄的顾客大都是些三三两两的散客，不过嘛，只要有酒，有朋友，人数多少又有什么关系呢？

traits.value: Light blue color matching short sleeves

name: Carter A
description: The truck cover is a large-character screen written by the deposed old party. Inside the truck are collections of works and books by Sansu, Qin Guan, and Huang Tingjian. The truckmen were ordered by their owners to push them to the suburbs and burn them. If they were literate, would they? Choose to hide some of these precious books?

chinese.name: 车夫甲
chinese.description: 货车盖布是废黜旧党书写的大字屏风，车内装着的是三苏、秦观、黄庭坚的文集、书籍，车夫们奉主人之命将推其去郊外焚毁，要是他们识字的话，会不会选择把这些珍贵的书籍藏起来一些呢？

name: The Pole-Carrying Servant
description: A servant, a little short, had been carrying a pole behind the lord's horse a long time ago. The thing picked on the pole is usually not too heavy, that is, it contains some cooking points that can be divided among several people.

chinese.name: 挑担仆人
chinese.description: 一个仆从，有些矮小，在很久以前就跟在老爷的马屁股后面挑扁担了。扁担上挑的东西通常不会太沉，也就是装着一些能够让数人分食的炊点而已。

name: The Drinking Customer
description:
An alcoholic leaning on the railing on the third floor was happily eating and drinking with his companions. The atmosphere seemed very warm.
"What does Li Taibai say about the poem? Jiufeng... confidant, it's a thousand cups less! You...you haven't, you haven't had enough. Xiao Er, how come your boiled water is tasteless! I'll just tell you the truth. Leave your broken shop and go to Tokyo for a good drink!"

chinese.name: 饮酒食客
chinese.description:
一位倚靠在三楼栏杆上正在与同伴欢畅共食共饮的酒客，气氛看似十分热烈。
“李太白那首诗怎么说来着？酒逢……知己啊，它千杯少！你……你可还没，喝够呢。小二，你这白开水怎么没有味啊！明个我就离开你这破店去东京喝好酒！”

name: Bystander A
description: When the shipwreck was about to happen, the spectators at the bridge head pointed, or exclaimed, enclosing the right side guardrail of the arch bridge, and several people tried to rescue them by crossing the railings. In fact, in this case, everyone is the same. In a panic, no one can tell whether they are helping or adding chaos.

chinese.name: 看客甲
chinese.description: 船难将发之时，桥头的看客或指指点点，或惊呼不已，把拱桥的右侧护栏围得水泄不通，有几个人越过栏杆企图施救，其实，这种情况下，所有人都是慌张的，他们是在帮忙，还是在添乱，没人分得清楚。

name: The Restaurant Waiter
description:
A man carrying tea utensils is preparing to add tea to the guests.
"The old customer in the middle drank too much again, so many of his friends are reliable. Ask me to quickly send this tea to the hangover, or I will get drunk in a while, I am afraid it will ruin the good things of other masters."

chinese.name: 店内伙计
chinese.description:
一位端着茶水用具的伙计，正准备给客人添茶。
“里间那位老主顾又喝多了，多得他朋友靠谱。托我赶紧把这茶水送去解解酒，不然一会发起酒疯来，怕是坏了其他老爷的好事。”

name: The Paraffin Oil Buyer
description:
A pedestrian with a longer lamp in his hand seems to be looking for something.
"Why can't even a hawker selling lamp oil be found in this market? It's just some liquor transporters. Can they still light up the lights at night with liquor?"

chinese.name: 买油行人
chinese.description:
一位手里拿着较长灯具的行人，似乎正在四处寻觅什么。
“这街市上怎么连个卖灯油的小贩都找不到？净是些运酒的，难道他们晚上还能拿酒点灯吗？”

name: The Inviting Scholar
description: A scribe respectfully invited the mistress to go out of the sedan chair to see the scenery. The posture is beautiful and polite, judging from the dressing of the crowd, the mistress in the sedan must also be of extraordinary origin.

chinese.name: 文士
chinese.description: 一位恭请女主人出轿看风景的文士。姿势端丽，形容有礼，从这一众人的穿着打扮来看，轿子里的女主人也必定出身不凡。

name: The Babycaring Maid
description:
A maid who helps the host’s family hold the young child and also travels with the host’s family.
"Master, do you think this flower branch is very beautiful? Hey, master, you can't move around. If you fall, you can't afford it."

chinese.name: 抱娃女佣
chinese.description:
一位帮主人家抱着幼童，同时也跟主人家共同出游的女佣。
“少爷，您看这花枝是不是很漂亮啊？哎，少爷您可不能乱动，若是摔将下来，奴婢可担当不起。”

name: Restaurant Guest C
description:
Business in this tea shop is booming, and the shop assistants are busy cleaning up. There is an endless stream of people who come to eat here, and a few guests are waiting for their refreshments to be served.
"Oh, I discovered the deliciousness of this store first, but now many arty people have come."

chinese.name: 食客丙
chinese.description:
这家茶肆生意正旺，店铺伙计正忙着收拾，来此处就餐的人络绎不绝，几个客人正在等待着他们的茶点端上来。
“呵，这家店的美味明明是我先发现的，现在却来了不少附庸风雅之徒。”

name: The Pole-Carrying Servant
description: A servant, a little short, had been carrying a pole behind the lord's horse a long time ago. The thing picked on the pole is usually not too heavy, that is, it contains some cooking points that can be divided among several people.

chinese.name: 挑担仆人
chinese.description: 一个仆从，有些矮小，在很久以前就跟在老爷的马屁股后面挑扁担了。扁担上挑的东西通常不会太沉，也就是装着一些能够让数人分食的炊点而已。

name: The Young Farmer
description: The farmer leaning on the branches for a short rest will not be long before he will return to farming in the fields. Now is the busy season of farming, I'm afraid there won't be too much time for him to rest.

chinese.name: 青年农夫
chinese.description: 倚靠着树枝稍作休息的农夫，过不了多久，他便会重新回到谷田中耕作。现在是农忙的季节，能够给他休息的时间恐怕不会太多。

name: The Cart Puller
description: A cart man. With a heavy face, he transported a car full of ink anthologies outside the city. The car was covered with calligraphy and painting. Underneath it was not known which literati scholar had worked hard. Just because one step was wrong, their calligraphy disappeared.

chinese.name: 推车人
chinese.description: 一位推车人。他面色沉重，将满车的墨迹文集运往城外，车上覆盖着字画，下面又不知是哪位文人学士的心血，只因一步踏错，他们的墨宝便从此不见天日。

name: The Cart Hauler
description: A car driver. He crouched on his back, and transported a car full of ink anthologies outside the city. The car was covered with calligraphy and painting. Underneath it was not known which literati scholar had worked hard. Only because one step was wrong, their calligraphy disappeared.

chinese.name: 牵车人
chinese.description: 一位牵车人。他佝偻着背，将满车的墨迹文集运往城外，车上覆盖着字画，下面又不知是哪位文人学士的心血，只因一步踏错，他们的墨宝便从此不见天日。

name: The Wine Cart Fella
description:
A buddy following the slow-moving donkey cart. He held the wine barrel in his hand, on the one hand for safety, and on the other hand, perhaps to avoid someone stealing the wine barrel.
"Hehe, this little devil, I am afraid that he will also be a drinker in the future. Then you can forget to help our business."

chinese.name: 伙计
chinese.description:
一位跟在慢悠悠行进的驴车后面的伙计。他手扶酒桶，一方面是为了安全，另一方面或许是避免有人来偷凿酒桶。
“呵呵，这小鬼头，将来怕也是嗜酒之人。到时候可忘了来帮衬我们的生意。”

traits.value: Sky blue color matching short sleeves

name: Restaurant Guest A
description:
Business in this tea shop is booming, and the shop assistants are busy cleaning up. There is an endless stream of people who come to eat here, and several guests are waiting for their refreshments to be served.
"That person is already eating, why haven't the refreshments I ordered come up yet?"

chinese.name: 食客甲
chinese.description:
这家茶肆生意正旺，店铺伙计正忙着收拾，来此处就餐的人络绎不绝，几个客人正在等待着他们的茶点端上来。
“那人都吃撑了，我点的茶点为什么还没上来？”

name: The Traveler on The Bridge
description: A tourist passing by the bridge pointed to the passenger ship in the distance in a panic. He didn't know what to do. There was a passenger ship approaching in the distance. Behind him, a large ship was rushing, and its mast almost ran into it. The bridge.

chinese.name: 桥上游客
chinese.description: 一个路过这座桥的游客，他惊慌的指着远方的客船，不知道如何是好，远方正有一艘客船驶来，而自己的身后，一艘大船正在抢险，它的桅杆差一点就撞上了桥梁。

name: The Treating Teenager
description:
A teenager who was pulled by his family to seek medical advice was attracted by the accident on the street and was quietly looking back.
"It's really weird, my lord, what's so good about that wine? After drinking it, I'm drunk and unreasonable. Now I'm going crazy before drinking it. Could it be that I will get drunk when I smell it?"

chinese.name: 就医少年
chinese.description:
一个被家里人拉来寻医问诊的少年被街上的事故吸引了视线，正在悄悄地回头围观。
“大人可真怪，那酒有什么好喝的？喝了以后醉醺醺地不讲道理。现在还没喝上就已经像在发酒疯了。莫不是闻到酒味都会醉？”

name: The Wine Carter
description:
An old man lazily driving a donkey cart. He held the whip of the car with a leisurely look. It seems that today is a good weather.
"Hey, the young people who are in a hurry to fetch the wine don't understand the taste of wine at all, they will just eat hazel and swallow it raw. This fine wine can be ruined."

chinese.name: 酒车车夫
chinese.description:
一位懒洋洋赶着驴车的老者。他举着车鞭，神色悠闲，看来今日是个好天气。
“哎，那些急着来取酒的年轻人根本不懂得品酒的滋味，只会胡吃海塞，生吞硬咽。这美酒，可都糟践喽。”

traits.value: Light green color matching short sleeves

name: The Lookers-On
description:
Xu is the old man who praised his ointment as a magical medicine, and there was a circle of people standing around, all of them listened carefully, and even the porter on the road looked distractedly.
"Why are there so many swindlers on this street, the hearts of the people are not old, and the hearts of the people are not old."

chinese.name: 围观看客
chinese.description:
许是这位老者把自己的药膏夸为神药，周围站了一圈人，个个听得认真，连赶路的挑夫都分神往这边张望。
“这大街上为何尽是些坑蒙拐骗之徒，人心不古，人心不古啊。”

name: The Bellman
description:
A watchman who was startled by the sound of the quarrel downstairs temporarily put down his work and looked downstairs to watch the excitement.
"The thoughts of the sir, we ordinary people really don't understand. During the day, we collect taxes on those coachmen as we please, and in the evening I want to call the watch on time. Although there are no culprits at night, the days are good. Let's go to sleep first. , I have to work at night."

chinese.name: 更夫
chinese.description:
一个被楼下吵架之声惊动了的更夫，暂时放下了手里的活计，探头向楼下看热闹。
“官老爷的心思，我们这些老百姓真是想不明白。白天对那些车夫随心所欲地收税，晚上又要我准时准点地打更。虽说现在夜晚也不见有贼人了，日子倒是不错。还是先睡罢，晚上还得做工。”

name: The Horse-Riding Master
description: A middle-aged scribe with a seemingly distinguished status and a laid-back posture, sitting on a tall horse with a happy spring breeze, leisurely, ready to step into this dazzling and lively capital.

chinese.name: 骑马主人
chinese.description: 一位看似身份尊贵，姿态悠闲的中年文士，坐在高头大马上一副春风得意的样子，悠悠闲闲，正准备迈入这让人目眩神迷的热闹京城。

name: The Clinic Doctor
description: A doctor in a doctor's shop who is treating children should be "Zhao Taicheng" written on the signboard of this doctor's shop. He looked serious and approachable. He bowed forward and explained the symptoms and medications to the visiting patients one by one.

chinese.name: 医铺大夫
chinese.description: 一位正在为小儿诊疗的医铺大夫，应当就是这间医铺招牌上写的“赵太丞”，只见他神色认真，姿态平易近人，躬身向前将病证用药等与来访病人一一说明。

name: Carter C
description: The truck cover is a large-character screen written by the deposed old party. Inside the truck are collections of works and books by Sansu, Qin Guan, and Huang Tingjian. The truckmen were ordered by their owners to push them to the suburbs and burn them. If they were literate, would they? Choose to hide some of these precious books?

chinese.description: 货车盖布是废黜旧党书写的大字屏风，车内装着的是三苏、秦观、黄庭坚的文集、书籍，车夫们奉主人之命将推其去郊外焚毁，要是他们识字的话，会不会选择把这些珍贵的书籍藏起来一些呢？

In fact, in this case, everyone is the same. In a panic, no one can tell whether they are helping or adding chaos.

chinese.description: 船难将发之时，桥头的看客或指指点点，或惊呼不已，把拱桥的右侧护栏围得水泄不通，有几个人越过栏杆企图施救，其实，这种情况下，所有人都是慌张的，他们是在帮忙，还是在添乱，没人分得清楚。

name: Sculler-Holding Boatman A
description:
Several boatmen joined together and used their best to hold a boat scull. The characteristic of this kind of boat is that there are two huge boat sculls at the fore and aft of the ship.
"Don't rush, I haven't seen any big winds and waves, don't overturn the boat in this calm river!"

chinese.name: 掌橹船夫甲
chinese.description:
几个船夫合在一起，用尽全力掌住了一只船橹，这种船的特点就在于船的首尾有两只巨大的船橹。
“动作不要急，老子什么大风大浪没见过，可别在这风平浪静的河里翻了船！”

traits.value: Light green color matching short sleeves

name: Idle Soldier A
description:
A group of soldiers on official business, but they are not mindful of their tasks, they just slouchy gathering outside the yamen, or sitting or lying down waiting for the officer to appear.
"Spring is sleepy and autumn is lacking, and summer is nap, and winter is March when I can't wake up. Every day is a good time to sleep."

chinese.name: 懒散士卒甲
chinese.description:
一群公务在身的士卒，但他们对于自己的任务并不上心，只是懒懒散散地聚在衙门外，或坐或躺地等待着长官出现。
“春困秋乏夏打盹，睡不醒的冬三月。每天都是睡觉的好时候。”

traits.value: Light blue color matching short sleeves

name: The Fan-Holding Scholar
description:
A white-clothed scribe holding a round fan, cast his gaze under his feet as he walked, as if he was thinking about something.
"It's also a fun thing to cross a horse in a day of leisure. The students who studied hard in the building reminded me of the day when I was the champion."

chinese.name: 持扇文士
chinese.description:
一位手持圆扇的白衣文士，边走边将视线投于脚下，似乎在思虑什么事。
“于闲暇之日跨马游街，亦是一桩趣事。那馆舍中苦读的学子，倒让我想起自己中状元的那日的盛况。”

name: The Clinic Doctor
description: A doctor in a doctor's shop who is treating children should be "Zhao Taicheng" written on the signboard of this doctor's shop. He looked serious and approachable. He bowed forward and explained the symptoms and medications to the visiting patients one by one.

chinese.name: 医铺大夫
chinese.description: 一位正在为小儿诊疗的医铺大夫，应当就是这间医铺招牌上写的“赵太丞”，只见他神色认真，姿态平易近人，躬身向前将病证用药等与来访病人一一说明。

traits.value: Light green color matching short sleeves

name: The Way-Asking Countryman
description: A countryman with a snack box in his hand is asking for directions in front of a large family. Looking at his clothes and packages, he should have come from the countryside to visit relatives and friends, and the guard kindly answered his questions and pointed out the direction. Looking along the direction of the guard's finger, maybe there is a bustling and bustling area outside the painting. world.

chinese.name: 问路的乡下人
chinese.description: 一位手提着点心匣子正在某位大户人家门前问路的乡下人。看他的穿着和包裹，应是从乡下赶来走亲访友，而守卫和善地回答了他的问题并指出方向，顺着守卫手指的方向看去，说不定画外有一片同样热闹繁华的世界。

name: The Beauty in Red
description:
A frivolous beauty in a red dress with a male crown and hat is putting his hand on the shoulder of the man beside him, seemingly inviting him back to the shop behind him to have a drink together.
"Officials, there is no feasting on firewood, rice, oil and salt, why don't we have a few drinks in the upstairs wing?"

chinese.name: 红衣美人
chinese.description:
一位带着男性冠帽，身着红衣的轻佻美人，正将手搭在一旁男子的肩上，似是邀请他回到身后的店里去共饮美酒。
“官人，柴米油盐哪有灯红酒绿美妙，不如我们到楼上厢房共饮几杯？”

name: The Fan-Holding Scholar
description:
A white-clothed scribe holding a round fan, cast his gaze under his feet as he walked, as if he was thinking about something.
"It's also a fun thing to cross a horse in a day of leisure. The students who studied hard in the building reminded me of the day when I was the champion."

chinese.name: 持扇文士
chinese.description:
一位手持圆扇的白衣文士，边走边将视线投于脚下，似乎在思虑什么事。
“于闲暇之日跨马游街，亦是一桩趣事。那馆舍中苦读的学子，倒让我想起自己中状元的那日的盛况。”

name: The Vendor
description:
A hawker holding a portable stand, looking around for a stall to support the stall.
"The wine-carrying carts are walking in a hurry. It's better to set up a stall in another place. It's not worth it to be knocked down.

chinese.name: 卖货小贩
chinese.description:
一位手持便携式支架，四处寻觅摊位以支起货摊的小贩。
“这运酒的车马走得真是急，还是换个地方摆摊得好，被撞倒可就不值当了。”

name: The Hotel Waiter
description: The guy at the foot shop is soliciting customers. He doesn’t know if he wants to be free or busy. Although the turnover of this hotel is not directly related to his wages, if the harvest is too bad, he may also be. Be driven away.

chinese.name: 酒店小二
chinese.description: 脚店的伙计，正在招揽顾客，也不知道他希望自己闲一些，还是希望忙一些，虽然说这间酒店的营业额跟自己的工钱没有直接关系，但要是收成太差了，自己也有可能会被赶走的吧。

name: The Discontent Bystander
description:
Xu is the old man who praised his ointment as a magical medicine, and there was a circle of people standing around, all of them listened carefully, and even the porter on the road looked distractedly.
"If this plaster is so amazing, it would be a good thing to buy one and go back to my father."

chinese.name: 不忿看客
chinese.description:
许是这位老者把自己的药膏夸为神药，周围站了一圈人，个个听得认真，连赶路的挑夫都分神往这边张望。
“若是这膏药真有如此神妙，买一帖回去给家父也是好事。”

name: The Luggage-Carrying Coachman
description: A horseman, carrying a bag of luggage, is chasing a runaway horse. Whether it is a horse or this bag of luggage, they are all existences that he cannot afford to lose. In other words, no matter what they are, they are much more valuable than him.

chinese.name: 拿着行李的马夫
chinese.description: 一个马夫，背着一包行李，正在追赶一匹脱缰的马。无论是马还是这包行李，都是他丢不得的存在，换句话说，无论那样的东西，都比他这人本身要有价值得多。

name: The Salt Store Owner
description: A private salt shop owner who is weighing the salt pile. The business in his shop looks deserted, but since salt was not a commodity that can be sold everywhere in the Northern Song Dynasty, the owner probably won’t worry about having no business to do-you see, now he is telling the salt pile with a smile on his face. It's a matter of discussion.

chinese.name: 盐铺店主
chinese.description: 一位正在给盐堆称重分量的私家盐铺店主。他的店内看起来生意冷清，不过鉴于盐在北宋并不是个可以随处售卖的商品，所以店主大概也并不会发愁没生意可做——您瞧，现在他正满脸喜色地给盐堆称斤论两呢。

name: Arguing Scholar B
description:
A scholar who had a good chat with people around him, he insisted so much that he reached out to comment on things under the bridge.
"You are not me, you know I don't know the joy of fish? Are you not imitating the sage?"

chinese.name: 争论书生乙
chinese.description:
一位与身边人聊得酣畅的书生，他十分坚持自己的意见，以至于伸手去评点桥下事物。
“子非我，安知我不知鱼之乐？你不也是一样在模仿先贤吗？”

name: The Palanquin-Carrying Servants
description: The two bearers carried the sedan chair with some difficulty. No matter how light the sedan chair is, it is a bit reluctant to carry it with only two people. What's more, the two sedan chairs look very thin, and this burden is a bit reluctant for them.

chinese.name: 抬轿仆人
chinese.description: 两个轿夫，有些困难地扛着轿子。再轻的轿子，只用两个人扛也有些勉强，更何况，这两个轿夫看上去十分瘦小的样子，这种重负对他们而言有些勉强。

name: Boatman B
description: The cruise ship is about to dock. The gunmen standing on the bow and the boatmen on the top of the boat are watching the right bank closely to prevent accidents. The accidents here mainly refer to the movement of the surrounding ships, and the direction and speed of the river. .

chinese.name: 船员乙
chinese.description: 游船即将靠岸，站在船头上的篙夫、船顶上的船夫们正密切注视着右岸，以防意外发生，这里的意外主要指的是周围的船只动向，已经河水的流动方向与速度。

name: The Tavern Waiter
description:
A man standing in front of the wine shop with a warm smile inviting pedestrians to come in to buy wine and have fun.
"Please from the guest officer! Oh, the king is here, as usual, right? I'll call them and bring you wine by the way!"

chinese.name: 迎客伙计
chinese.description:
一位带着热情笑容站在酒坊门前邀请行人进来买酒玩乐的伙计。
“客官里边儿请！哟，王员外来啦，照旧对吧？我这就去喊她们，顺便给您拿酒去！”

name: The Bargaining Drinker
description:
A man who is bargaining with vegetable farmers seems to have a lot of relationship with the woman in red around him.
"Don't shout, you can't sell this dish cheaply? My wife gave me such a little money. Oh, Xiaohong, you go up and wait, the big deal this time I can buy you a few more glasses!"

chinese.name: 正店酒客
chinese.description:
一位正在与菜农讨价还价的男子，似与身边的红衣女子关系匪浅。
“别吆喝了，你这菜就不能便宜点卖？我家夫人可就给了我这么点钱。哦，小红啊，你先上去候着，大不了这次我可得多请你几杯！”

name: Confucian Student A
description: A Confucian scholar who came to solve hexagrams and ask characters. He leaned forward, his face was eager, ready to hear from her husband a bright future with a lot of flowers, it doesn't matter if he doesn't, he has money, but the future must sound reliable.

chinese.name: 儒生甲
chinese.description: 一位上门解卦问字的儒生。他上身前倾，面露急切，准备从先生那里听得一个花团锦簇的大好前程，没有也没关系，钱他有的是，但前程一定要听起来靠谱。

name: The Palanquin-Carrier of The Civil Official
description: On the bridge, the sedan-servant and the horse-riding military officer did not give way to each other. Under their sign, the bearers and horsemen on both sides relied on their masters, making noisiness. Humility is a fine culture that has existed since ancient times, but at that time, most people I have forgotten all this, just thinking about getting ahead and stepping on others.

chinese.name: 文官轿夫
chinese.description: 桥上坐轿文官和骑马武官互不相让，在他们的示意下，两边的轿夫与马夫各仗其主，吵闹不休，谦卑是自古以来便存在的优良文化，但在那时，大多数人都忘记了这些，只想着出人头地，把别人踩在脚下。

name: The Tavern Waiter
description:
A man standing in front of the wine shop with a warm smile inviting pedestrians to come in to buy wine and have fun.
"Please from the guest officer! Oh, the king is here, as usual, right? I'll call them and bring you wine by the way!"

chinese.name: 迎客伙计
chinese.description:
一位带着热情笑容站在酒坊门前邀请行人进来买酒玩乐的伙计。
“客官里边儿请！哟，王员外来啦，照旧对吧？我这就去喊她们，顺便给您拿酒去！”

name: The Inn Owner
description:
An inn owner who was talking to the owner of the furniture store next door in front of the billboard in his shop. As can be seen from his signboard, this hotel is still an honest and reliable time-honored hotel, which is worthy of trust.
"Old Li, what new gadgets have you bought? Recently, a rich kid came to my hotel to study. The shot was called a magnanimous person. Is there any strange gadget to sell him?

chinese.name: 旅店主人
chinese.description:
一位正在自家店铺广告牌前与隔壁家具店老板交谈的旅店主人。从他的招牌上可以看出，这家还是诚信可靠的老字号旅店，值得信赖。
“老李，又进了什么新玩意？最近有个富家子弟来我这住店读书，出手那叫一个阔绰，有没有什么稀奇玩意让我卖他？

name: The Smuggler
description: The smugglers who supervised the workers to carry the grain. None of the grain ships was an official ship, and there was no grain officer. The court has lost the opportunity to store and transport the national grain. Obviously, this smuggler will only let the shipmen carry the grain. Moved to your own private warehouse.

chinese.name: 走私商
chinese.description: 监督工人们搬运粮食的走私商贩，这些运粮船中没有一条官船，也没有督粮官，朝廷已丢失国粮储运的机会，显而易见的，这位走私商只会让这些船工们将粮食搬往自己的私仓。

name: The Herb-Drinks Vendor
description: A fragrant drinker vendor introducing his own drinks to customers. You see, our drink can not only relieve heat and heat, but also dispel dampness and detoxification. It can also strengthen the body and cure all kinds of diseases. After drinking it, it is very cool, two mouthfuls, three mouthfuls, bright, four mouthfuls ...Guests, would you like to try?

chinese.name: 香饮子摊贩
chinese.description: 一位在给客人介绍自家饮品的香饮子摊贩。您看，咱家的饮子不仅能解暑消热，还能祛湿排毒，还能强身健体，还能包治百病，喝下去一口透心凉，两口心飞扬，三口心明眼亮，四口……客人您要不试试？

name: A Father and A Son
description: Father, who is shopping with his children, is asking a hawker about the hand-made toys he has made. Although I really can’t see the fun of such gadgets, as long as the children can be happy, it will be fine. .

chinese.name: 一对父子
chinese.description: 带着孩子一起逛街的父亲，正在向一个小贩询问关于他出手的手制玩具，虽然说实在是看不出来这样的小玩意到底有什么好玩的，但只要小孩子能开心，怎么样都好了。

name: Silk Store Customer B
description:
A customer who is sitting sideways on a silk paving bench seems to be comparing the details of the product.
"I said the shopkeeper, the shop is bullying. Why do you hide this fine silk so deep? It's specially left for me? People are always treacherous and slippery, so I have to look for them again."

chinese.name: 帛铺顾客乙
chinese.description:
一位侧坐在帛铺长凳上，似乎正在对比商品细节的顾客。
“我说掌柜的，店大欺客啊。怎么把这上好的绸子藏得这么深？专门给我留下的？人老奸马老滑，我可得再找找看。”

name: The Pole-Carrying Servant
description: A servant, a little short, had been carrying a pole behind the lord's horse a long time ago. The thing picked on the pole is usually not too heavy, that is, it contains some cooking points that can be divided among several people.

chinese.name: 挑担仆人
chinese.description: 一个仆从，有些矮小，在很久以前就跟在老爷的马屁股后面挑扁担了。扁担上挑的东西通常不会太沉，也就是装着一些能够让数人分食的炊点而已。

name: The Flower Buyer
description: A flower buyer who is carefully picking flowers and branches is ready to choose the flowers that suit his wishes and go home to decorate the courtyard. Commercial marketing among the flower sellers can be ignored, and the quality of the flower branches should be carefully selected.

chinese.name: 买花人
chinese.description: 一位正在仔细挑拣花枝的买花人，准备挑选了符合心意的花回家装点门院。卖花人口中的商业营销可以不放在心上，花枝的质量要好好挑选。

name: Teahouse Guest A
description: A pedestrian who took a break in the teahouse, but the donkey was frightened and struggling with the rope desperately, so that he could only let go of the idea of ​​rest. And the reason why the donkey was frightened was that the horse on the side of the road was also frightened. It was a noisy day.

chinese.name: 茶客甲
chinese.description: 在茶馆中稍作歇息的行路人，但驴因为受到惊吓而拼命地拉着绳子挣扎，使得他只能放下休息的念头。而驴受惊的原因，是隔着路一旁的马也受惊了，真是喧闹的一天啊。

name: The Toy Vendor
description: Straw hat vendors peddling toys along the street are explaining to a father and son about the toys they woven. The materials for making toys are very cheap and the method of making them is quite simple, but they can easily attract children who are curious about everything in the world. .

chinese.name: 小贩
chinese.description: 沿街兜售玩具的草帽小贩，正在向一对父子讲解自己编织的玩具，这样的玩具制作材料十分廉价，制作方法也相当简单，但就是能很轻而易举地吸引到对世界的一切都充满好奇的小孩子。

name: Restaurant Guest B
description:
Business in this tea shop is booming, and the shop assistants are busy cleaning up. There is an endless stream of people who come to eat here, and a few guests are waiting for their refreshments to be served.
"With so many people coming to this shop, refreshments must not be wrong, so that I am also a member of the upper class."

chinese.name: 食客乙
chinese.description:
这家茶肆生意正旺，店铺伙计正忙着收拾，来此处就餐的人络绎不绝，几个客人正在等待着他们的茶点端上来。
“这么多人来这家店，茶点一定错不了，这样我也是上流的一员了。”

name: Sculler-Holding  Boatman B
description:
Several boatmen joined together and used their best to hold a boat scull. The characteristic of this kind of boat is that there are two huge boat sculls at the fore and aft of the ship.
"(I always feel that someone is trying to reverse it, otherwise the boat would not be so slow.)"

chinese.name: 掌橹船夫乙
chinese.description:
几个船夫合在一起，用尽全力掌住了一只船橹，这种船的特点就在于船的首尾有两只巨大的船橹。
“（总觉得有人使力使反了，不然船不至于这么慢。）”

traits.value: Sky blue color matching short sleeves

name: The Buyer
description:
A pedestrian with a delicate object in his hand seems to have just patronized the trader's business.
"Hey, don't tell me, this old man really has some strange things, and I don't know where he got it from."

chinese.name: 买货行人
chinese.description:
一位手里拿着精巧物件的行人，似是刚光顾过货郎的生意。
“嗨，你还别说，这老头还真有些稀奇玩意，也不知道他是从哪里淘来的。”

name: The Rest-Taking Boatman
description: After the cargo ship arrived and the cargo was safely unloaded, a crew member was lying on the roof and enjoying a short rest time comfortably. The rest time was not sufficient, and there was no way for him to do other things, so he just lay on the ship and watched. It's quite interesting under the boat.

chinese.name: 小憩船员
chinese.description: 货船到岸，安全卸货后，一名船员正趴在顶棚上惬意地享用着短暂的休息时间，休息的时间并不充裕，没办法让他去做一些其他的事，也就趴在船上，看着船下还算有些意思。

name: Chatting Teahouse Guest, A
description:
In a tea shop by the Bian River, a few tea customers are gathering together, drinking tea and chatting, very comfortable.
"People nowadays care about buying wine and eating, how can we taste tea in a tea shop so elegantly as a few of us."

chinese.name: 闲聊茶客甲
chinese.description:
在汴河边的一家茶坊里，几个茶客正聚在一起，一边饮茶，一边闲聊，十分惬意。
“现在的人净顾着买酒吃，哪像我们几个这么高雅地在茶铺品茶。”

name: The Smuggler
description: The smugglers who supervised the workers to carry the grain. None of the grain ships was an official ship, and there was no grain officer. The court has lost the opportunity to store and transport the national grain. Obviously, this smuggler will only let the shipmen carry the grain. Moved to your own private warehouse.

chinese.name: 走私商
chinese.description: 监督工人们搬运粮食的走私商贩，这些运粮船中没有一条官船，也没有督粮官，朝廷已丢失国粮储运的机会，显而易见的，这位走私商只会让这些船工们将粮食搬往自己的私仓。

name: Troubled Carter A
description: The two coachmen pressed forward and dragged them in an attempt to reduce the inertia of the vehicle’s sliding. The donkey’s advancing inertia made it difficult to control itself. It staggered. It turned its head to avoid the trafficker. It was dangerous. In modern terms, their car was obviously Already overweight.

chinese.name: 避险车夫甲
chinese.description: 两个车夫前压后拽，企图减轻车辆下滑的惯性，毛驴前进的惯性使它难以自控，打着趔趄，它侧首回避贩夫，可谓险象环生，用现代的话来说，他们的车显然是已经超重了。

name: The Audience
description:
A listener who stands relatively outside and looks very serious may be dismissive of the content of the dialogue book.
"Oh, people in the market, even if the tongue is bright and the lotus flower will only be sensational. What's so good about this? I'll leave after listening to this paragraph!"

chinese.name: 听众
chinese.description:
一位站得比较靠外，表情也非常严肃的听众，或许是对话本的内容不屑一顾。
“呵，市井之徒，就算舌灿莲花也只会哗众取宠。这有什么好听的？听完这段我就走！”

name: Warning Boatman B
description: Seeing that the big ship is in distress, the boatmen standing on the tops of the boats moored on both sides of the canal are giving out loud warnings, in case the bow or stern of the passenger ship will accidentally collide when adjusting the direction. If two ships of this kind of draught collide Together, the consequences will be disastrous.

chinese.name: 示警船工乙
chinese.description: 眼看大船遇险，运河两岸停泊的船顶上都站着船工在大声发出警示，以防这艘客船的船头或船尾在调整方向时会意外撞上来，这这种吃水量的两艘船一旦撞在一起，后果将不堪设想。

name: The Rest-Taking Porter
description: Carrying a pole, the porter passing by here, faced with the warm pasta, he decided to temporarily put down the burden on his shoulders. Maybe he is not hungry now, but his mouth is a bit greedy. Anyway, this kind of pastry won't cost much. .

chinese.name: 小憩挑夫
chinese.description: 挑着扁担，路过此地的挑夫，面对热乎乎的面食，他决定暂时放下肩上的担子，也许他现在并不饿，只是嘴巴有点馋而已，反正这种面点也不会贵到哪里去。

name: The Old Shaving Man
description:
An old man is holding a squeegee and shaves and cleans the face of a customer on the side of the street. This should be the earliest beauty shop to appear in Chinese paintings.
"The guest officer don’t need to be afraid. The old man is sculpted on the flesh, and the knife is used to blend the three schools of Yanjing, Qizhou, and Yangzhou. The heads in this city of Bianjing have been subdued by the old man’s craftsmanship. Hey! Guest officer, don’t move around. The young people nowadays don't have the courage at all, isn't it just a shave?"

chinese.name: 修面翁
chinese.description:
一个老人正手持刮刀，在街侧为顾客刮脸清面，这应该是中国绘画作品中出现的最早的美容店。
“客官不必害怕，老夫江湖诨号肉上雕花，刀法融燕京齐州扬州三派，这汴京城里的头颅都在老夫的手艺之下折服过。哎！客官你别乱动啊！现在的年轻人，一点胆气都没有，不就是修个面嘛？”

name: The Passing-By Wooden-Luggage Porter
description:
A pedestrian carrying two wooden boxes on a pole, judging from the arc of the pole, the two boxes may not weigh much, but they don't know what they are inside.
"This literati is also hypocritical. A little bit of goods can't be carried by a horse directly. But I can make a few glasses of wine."

chinese.name: 挑担行人
chinese.description:
一位用扁担挑着两个木箱的行人，从扁担的弧度来看这两只箱子或许无甚重量，只是不知里面当是何物。
“这文人也是矫情，些许点货物就不能直接让马扛着。不过我倒是可以借此赚几杯酒钱。”

name: The Luggage-Carrying Coachman
description: A horseman, carrying a bag of luggage, is chasing a runaway horse. Whether it is a horse or this bag of luggage, they are all existences that he cannot afford to lose. In other words, no matter what they are, they are much more valuable than him.

chinese.name: 拿着行李的马夫
chinese.description: 一个马夫，背着一包行李，正在追赶一匹脱缰的马。无论是马还是这包行李，都是他丢不得的存在，换句话说，无论那样的东西，都比他这人本身要有价值得多。

name: The Easy Porter
description: A porter who followed the master's sedan chair, with not too many things on his back, made his footsteps easy and pleasant, and he even had free time to scold other people who were struggling on the road.

chinese.name: 轻松挑夫
chinese.description: 一位跟随在主人轿子身后的挑夫，背负着不太多的东西，这使得他的脚步还算轻松愉快，甚至有闲暇时间去呵斥走在这路上的其他苦命人。

name: Traveler C
description: Tourists traveling in twos and threes, they may come out for a walk or go shopping, but now they have a dispute over where to go next. One wants to go east and one wants to go west. , There is another person who wants to stay on the bridge.

chinese.name: 游客丙
chinese.description: 三三两两结伴同游的游客们，他们可能是出来散步的，也可能是出来购物的，但现在，他们为接下来往那边走发生了争执，一个人想要往东，一个人想要去西，还有一个人想要留在桥上。

name: The Palanquin-Carrier
description: A bearer who has just put down a heavy sedan chair, no matter how comfortable the people in the sedan chair are, this kind of action tool still needs manpower to carry.

chinese.name: 轿夫
chinese.description: 一位刚刚把沉重的轿子放下来的轿夫，不管在轿子里的人有多么安逸，这种行动工具终究还是需要人力来背负的。

name: Traveler B
description: Tourists traveling in twos and threes, they may come out for a walk or go shopping, but now they have a dispute over where to go next. One wants to go east and one wants to go west. , There is another person who wants to stay on the bridge.

chinese.name: 游客乙
chinese.description: 三三两两结伴同游的游客们，他们可能是出来散步的，也可能是出来购物的，但现在，他们为接下来往那边走发生了争执，一个人想要往东，一个人想要去西，还有一个人想要留在桥上。

name: The Cake Stand Owner
description: A bakery owner who is introducing his newly-baked biscuits to his guests. Guest officer, our roasted duck, roasted young chicken, roasted goose sauce, chicken, bacon, Songhua tripe, bacon, sausage, assorted Supan, smoked chicken tripe-it doesn’t have any, but we have a new hot cake. How about a piece?

chinese.name: 饼铺老板
chinese.description: 一位正在向客人介绍自家新出炉胡饼的饼铺老板。客官，我们这烧花鸭烧雏鸡烧子鹅酱鸡腊肉松花小肚腊肉香肠什锦苏盘熏鸡白肚——它都没有，但我们有新出炉的热饼，来一块如何？

name: The Walking-By Porter
description: For passers-by passing by, the newly opened restaurant by the pier attracted his attention, but did not stop him. A store with gorgeous decorations like this must be something you can't afford to patronize.

chinese.name: 行路挑夫
chinese.description: 路过此地的行路人，码头边新开的饭馆吸引了他的眼光，却并没有让他停下脚步，像这样装潢华丽的门店，相必是自己这种扁担客光顾不起的吧。

name: Water Carrier B
description: A water picker who is about to put the bucket into the well. He and the water picker next to him seem to have formed a very reasonable water picking process, from picking water to delivering water.

chinese.name: 挑水者乙
chinese.description: 一位正准备将水桶放进井中的挑水者。他和旁边的挑水者似乎共同组成了个十分合理的挑水流程，从打水到送水一条龙服务。

name: The Paper Horse Vendor
description: A stall owner who opened the sale of paper horses and artifacts on the Ching Ming Festival, his complexion seemed to be thinking about today’s business: Although it is now the time to sell these goods, all the pedestrians do not look here. These paper-horse paper-men are not easy to yell, so what should they do if they have been exposed to moisture for a long time.

chinese.name: 纸马摊贩
chinese.description: 一位在清明节开张售卖冥器纸马的摊主，面色沉凝，似是在思索今日生意：虽说现在正是卖这些货物的时候，可这往来行人，一个个眼神都不往这边瞅，这些纸马纸人又不好吆喝，放久受了潮气又该如何是好。

name: Barge Hauler B
description: In the dimness in the distance, five trackers pulled the big ship upstream, exhausting all their strength, trying to pull the luxurious passenger ship to the dock. At the end of the rope, the gunman standing on the bow, the owner and the boatman on the top of the ship are watching the right bank closely.

chinese.name: 纤夫乙
chinese.description: 在远处的朦胧中，五个纤夫拉着大船逆流而上，用尽浑身力气，试着将豪华的客船拉向码头。纤绳的尽头，站在船头上的篙夫、船顶上的船主、船夫正密切注视着右岸。

name: Carter A
description: The truck cover is a large-character screen written by the deposed old party. Inside the truck are collections of works and books by Sansu, Qin Guan, and Huang Tingjian. The truckmen were ordered by their owners to push them to the suburbs and burn them. If they were literate, would they? Choose to hide some of these precious books?

chinese.name: 车夫甲
chinese.description: 货车盖布是废黜旧党书写的大字屏风，车内装着的是三苏、秦观、黄庭坚的文集、书籍，车夫们奉主人之命将推其去郊外焚毁，要是他们识字的话，会不会选择把这些珍贵的书籍藏起来一些呢？

name: Water Carrier B
description: A water picker who is about to put the bucket into the well. He and the water picker next to him seem to have formed a very reasonable water picking process, from picking water to delivering water.

chinese.name: 挑水者乙
chinese.description: 一位正准备将水桶放进井中的挑水者。他和旁边的挑水者似乎共同组成了个十分合理的挑水流程，从打水到送水一条龙服务。

name: The Smuggler
description: The smugglers who supervised the workers to carry the grain. None of the grain ships was an official ship, and there was no grain officer. The court has lost the opportunity to store and transport the national grain. Obviously, this smuggler will only let the shipmen carry the grain. Moved to your own private warehouse.

chinese.name: 走私商
chinese.description: 监督工人们搬运粮食的走私商贩，这些运粮船中没有一条官船，也没有督粮官，朝廷已丢失国粮储运的机会，显而易见的，这位走私商只会让这些船工们将粮食搬往自己的私仓。

name: The Following Servant
description: A servant with his master's handy things followed behind the master's horse. His work was obviously much easier than that of the porter behind him, which made his steps and expressions look quite brisk.

chinese.name: 仆人
chinese.description: 一位带着主人随身轻巧物件的仆人，跟随在主人的马匹身后，他的活计明显比身后那位挑夫要轻松多了，这使他的步伐和表情看起来也相当轻快。

name: The Rich Student
description: One imperial examination, ten years of simulation. This is a rich student who is studying indoors on a railing. He can afford to rent a room for one hundred words a day. He is not ashamed of his pocket, and he is willing to use a better environment to match his talents.

chinese.name: 富家学子
chinese.description: 一朝科举，十年模拟。这是一位正在室内凭栏苦读的富家学子，他能租得起每天一百文的房间，想来囊中并不羞涩，且愿意用更好的环境来匹配上自己的才华。

traits.value: Sky blue color matching short sleeves

name: The Herb-Drinks Vendor
description: A fragrant drinker vendor introducing his own drinks to customers. You see, our drink can not only relieve heat and heat, but also dispel dampness and detoxification. It can also strengthen the body and cure all kinds of diseases. After drinking it, it is very cool, two mouthfuls, three mouthfuls, bright, four mouthfuls ...Guests, would you like to try?

chinese.name: 香饮子摊贩
chinese.description: 一位在给客人介绍自家饮品的香饮子摊贩。您看，咱家的饮子不仅能解暑消热，还能祛湿排毒，还能强身健体，还能包治百病，喝下去一口透心凉，两口心飞扬，三口心明眼亮，四口……客人您要不试试？

name: The Herb-Drinks Vendor
description: A fragrant drinker vendor introducing his own drinks to customers. You see, our drink can not only relieve heat and heat, but also dispel dampness and detoxification. It can also strengthen the body and cure all kinds of diseases. After drinking it, it is very cool, two mouthfuls, three mouthfuls, bright, four mouthfuls ...Guests, would you like to try?

chinese.name: 香饮子摊贩
chinese.description: 一位在给客人介绍自家饮品的香饮子摊贩。您看，咱家的饮子不仅能解暑消热，还能祛湿排毒，还能强身健体，还能包治百病，喝下去一口透心凉，两口心飞扬，三口心明眼亮，四口……客人您要不试试？

name: The Prayer-Holding Host
description: A host holding a prayer to send guests farewell is ordering a man to kill the sheep and pray to the Taoist god to protect the guests from traveling safely. Standing on the side of the road, he sent the most sincere blessings to the guests who used to live in his own home, wishing him a smooth journey.

chinese.name: 送客主人
chinese.description: 一位手持祷文送客人离别远行的主人，正在命令伙计杀羊祈求道神保佑客人远行平安。他站在道路一边，对曾经借住自己家的客人送上最真挚的祝福，祝福他远游一路顺风。

name: Restaurant Guest C
description:
Business in this tea shop is booming, and the shop assistants are busy cleaning up. There is an endless stream of people who come to eat here, and a few guests are waiting for their refreshments to be served.
"Oh, I discovered the deliciousness of this store first, but now many arty people have come."

chinese.name: 食客丙
chinese.description:
这家茶肆生意正旺，店铺伙计正忙着收拾，来此处就餐的人络绎不绝，几个客人正在等待着他们的茶点端上来。
“呵，这家店的美味明明是我先发现的，现在却来了不少附庸风雅之徒。”

name: Sculler-Holding Boatman A
description:
Several boatmen joined together and used their best to hold a boat scull. The characteristic of this kind of boat is that there are two huge boat sculls at the fore and aft of the ship.
"Don't rush, I haven't seen any big winds and waves, don't overturn the boat in this calm river!"

chinese.name: 掌橹船夫甲
chinese.description:
几个船夫合在一起，用尽全力掌住了一只船橹，这种船的特点就在于船的首尾有两只巨大的船橹。
“动作不要急，老子什么大风大浪没见过，可别在这风平浪静的河里翻了船！”

name: Fortune Teller A
description: A fortune teller holding a hexagram banner is calculating his fate for a man, and there are people watching him sideways. In fact, it is not so much fortune telling, but rather guessing what the person wants to hear in front of him.

chinese.name: 算命先生甲
chinese.description: 一个手举卦旗的算命先生，正在为一个汉子测算他的命运，旁边还有人在侧身观看，实际上，与其说是在算命，倒不如说是在猜测面前这个人想要听一些什么话。

name: The Vegetable Farmer
description:
A vegetable farmer who is selling his own vegetables to customers is eloquent and eloquent.
"Coriander, spicy green peppers, green onions, baby celery, lentils, eggplants, cucumbers, winter melons, large sea stalks, radishes, carrots, flat radishes, sprouts of toon, garlic, good leeks! Lord, you want What can I do?"

chinese.name: 菜农
chinese.description:
一位正在向客人售卖自家菜的菜农，口若悬河，滔滔不绝。
“香菜、辣青椒、勾葱、嫩芹菜、扁豆、茄子、黄瓜、架冬瓜、卖大海茄、卖萝卜、胡萝卜、扁萝卜、嫩芽的香椿、蒜儿来、好韭菜！这位爷您要来点什么？”

name: The Bending Bystander
description:
Xu is the old man who praised his ointment as a magical medicine, and there was a circle of people standing around, all of them listened carefully, and even the porter on the road looked distractedly.
"Oh, old god, this plaster is so good, why don't you use it first?"

chinese.name: 屈腰看客
chinese.description:
许是这位老者把自己的药膏夸为神药，周围站了一圈人，个个听得认真，连赶路的挑夫都分神往这边张望。
“哟，老神仙，这膏药这么灵，你咋不先用呢？”

name: The Restaurant Owner
description: The owner of this wharf restaurant is using a long rod to adjust the position of the colored forging. These colored forgings have added some lively atmosphere to the shop. Even the ancients thousands of years ago have realized that the decoration of the facade is important for the business in the store. importance.

chinese.name: 饭店店主
chinese.description: 这家码头饭馆的店主正在用一顶长杆调整彩锻位置，这几条彩锻为店铺增加了些热闹的气氛，即便是数千年前的古人，也已经意识到了门面装点对于店内生意的重要性。

name: The Teenage Farmer
description: The young man who was not in his hair-cutting year led the donkey team composed of five donkeys and came to the prosperous Bianjing full of charcoal. Maybe it was for life or to sell in the city.

chinese.name: 少年农夫
chinese.description: 不及束发之年的少年，在由五只驴组成的驴队之前牵头，驼着满满当当的木炭走向繁华的汴京，也许是生活之用，也许为了到城里售卖。

traits.value: Light blue color matching short sleeves

name: Bystander B
description: When the shipwreck was about to happen, the spectators at the bridge head pointed, or exclaimed, enclosing the right side guardrail of the arch bridge, and several people tried to rescue them by crossing the railings. In fact, in this case, everyone is the same. In a panic, no one can tell whether they are helping or adding chaos.

chinese.name: 看客乙
chinese.description: 船难将发之时，桥头的看客或指指点点，或惊呼不已，把拱桥的右侧护栏围得水泄不通，有几个人越过栏杆企图施救，其实，这种情况下，所有人都是慌张的，他们是在帮忙，还是在添乱，没人分得清楚。

name: The Smuggler
description: The smugglers who supervised the workers to carry the grain. None of the grain ships was an official ship, and there was no grain officer. The court has lost the opportunity to store and transport the national grain. Obviously, this smuggler will only let the shipmen carry the grain. Moved to your own private warehouse.

chinese.name: 走私商
chinese.description: 监督工人们搬运粮食的走私商贩，这些运粮船中没有一条官船，也没有督粮官，朝廷已丢失国粮储运的机会，显而易见的，这位走私商只会让这些船工们将粮食搬往自己的私仓。

name: The Treating Teenager
description:
A teenager who was pulled by his family to seek medical advice was attracted by the accident on the street and was quietly looking back.
"It's really weird, my lord, what's so good about that wine? After drinking it, I'm drunk and unreasonable. Now I'm going crazy before drinking it. Could it be that I will get drunk when I smell it?"

chinese.name: 就医少年
chinese.description:
一个被家里人拉来寻医问诊的少年被街上的事故吸引了视线，正在悄悄地回头围观。
“大人可真怪，那酒有什么好喝的？喝了以后醉醺醺地不讲道理。现在还没喝上就已经像在发酒疯了。莫不是闻到酒味都会醉？”

name: Idle Soldier C
description:
A group of soldiers on official business, but they are not mindful of their tasks, they just slouchy gathering outside the yamen, or sitting or lying down waiting for the officer to appear.
"Don't speak loudly, let the master continue to sleep. If he continues to sleep, we can continue to rest."

chinese.name: 懒散士卒丙
chinese.description:
一群公务在身的士卒，但他们对于自己的任务并不上心，只是懒懒散散地聚在衙门外，或坐或躺地等待着长官出现。
“别大声说话，让老爷继续睡，他继续睡，我们就能继续歇着。”

name: Silk Store Customer A
description:
A wealthy customer sitting on a silk shop bench is concentrating on consulting the shop owner about the question of silk and satin.
"I heard that the silks and satin in your shop are the best in the city? Then wrap all your best silks and satin for me. Why do you need change? Take this silver bullion and don't have to look for it."

chinese.name: 帛铺顾客甲
chinese.description:
一位坐在帛铺长凳上，正在专心向店老板咨询绸缎问题的有钱顾客。
“听说你这店里的绸缎是全城最好的？那就把你最好的绸缎都包好给我。怎么还要零钱，这锭银子拿去，不用找了。”

name: The Accompanying Women
description: A woman accompanying her, perhaps another family member of the sick child, stood by and anxiously told the doctor about the poor child's illness.

chinese.name: 陪侍妇人
chinese.description: 一位陪伴在旁侧的妇人，或许是得病孩子的另一位家人，站立在一旁，焦急地向大夫诉说这可怜孩子的病症。

name: Chatting Teahouse Guest, A
description:
In a tea shop by the Bian River, a few tea customers are gathering together, drinking tea and chatting, very comfortable.
"People nowadays care about buying wine and eating, how can we taste tea in a tea shop so elegantly as a few of us."

chinese.name: 闲聊茶客甲
chinese.description:
在汴河边的一家茶坊里，几个茶客正聚在一起，一边饮茶，一边闲聊，十分惬意。
“现在的人净顾着买酒吃，哪像我们几个这么高雅地在茶铺品茶。”

name: Servant A
description:
At the entrance of the tea shop, a guest slowly climbed up the back of the donkey. Xu Shi had just finished eating and planned to ride the donkey home. His servants were asking him to ride the donkey.
"(Which way is there to taste tea with rice in tea, so it's weird not to eat it.)"

chinese.name: 侍从甲
chinese.description:
茶肆门口有客人缓慢地往驴背上爬，许是刚吃完饭，打算骑驴回家，他的仆从们正在招呼他骑上驴。
“（哪有用茶泡饭的品茗方法，这样不吃撑才怪。）”

name: The Prayer-Holding Host
description: A host holding a prayer to send guests farewell is ordering a man to kill the sheep and pray to the Taoist god to protect the guests from traveling safely. Standing on the side of the road, he sent the most sincere blessings to the guests who used to live in his own home, wishing him a smooth journey.

chinese.name: 送客主人
chinese.description: 一位手持祷文送客人离别远行的主人，正在命令伙计杀羊祈求道神保佑客人远行平安。他站在道路一边，对曾经借住自己家的客人送上最真挚的祝福，祝福他远游一路顺风。

name: The Salt Store Owner
description: A private salt shop owner who is weighing the salt pile. The business in his shop looks deserted, but since salt was not a commodity that can be sold everywhere in the Northern Song Dynasty, the owner probably won’t worry about having no business to do-you see, now he is telling the salt pile with a smile on his face. It's a matter of discussion.

chinese.name: 盐铺店主
chinese.description: 一位正在给盐堆称重分量的私家盐铺店主。他的店内看起来生意冷清，不过鉴于盐在北宋并不是个可以随处售卖的商品，所以店主大概也并不会发愁没生意可做——您瞧，现在他正满脸喜色地给盐堆称斤论两呢。

name: Sculling Boatman B
description: Several boatmen were divided into two groups, left and right, and shook the big scull. The boatmen’s hard work and optimism are vividly remembered. It seems that they can hear rhythmic horns. It is quite difficult to shake such a big scull, but these boatmen still Didn't find it difficult.

chinese.name: 摇橹船夫乙
chinese.description: 数个船夫分左右两组奋力摇着大橹驶向前方，船工们的辛劳和乐观历历在目，似乎能听到有节奏的号子声，摇动这样的大橹相当费力，但这些船夫们还没有觉得多么困难。

name: The Touring Scholar
description:
A scholar who stretched out his hand and pointed at the fishes downstream of the bridge and judged loudly.
"The fish in the water are free and happy, but unfortunately, they only know the pleasure of the water, but they still don't understand the pleasure of tourists."

chinese.name: 游玩书生
chinese.description:
一位伸出手来对着桥下游鱼指指点点大声评断的书生。
“这水中的鱼儿倒是自由快乐，可惜，它们只知道水中之乐，却还是不懂游人的乐趣。”

name: The Hotel Waiter
description: The guy at the foot shop is soliciting customers. He doesn’t know if he wants to be free or busy. Although the turnover of this hotel is not directly related to his wages, if the harvest is too bad, he may also be. Be driven away.

chinese.name: 酒店小二
chinese.description: 脚店的伙计，正在招揽顾客，也不知道他希望自己闲一些，还是希望忙一些，虽然说这间酒店的营业额跟自己的工钱没有直接关系，但要是收成太差了，自己也有可能会被赶走的吧。

name: The Traveler on The Bridge
description: A tourist passing by the bridge pointed to the passenger ship in the distance in a panic. He didn't know what to do. There was a passenger ship approaching in the distance. Behind him, a large ship was rushing, and its mast almost ran into it. The bridge.

chinese.name: 桥上游客
chinese.description: 一个路过这座桥的游客，他惊慌的指着远方的客船，不知道如何是好，远方正有一艘客船驶来，而自己的身后，一艘大船正在抢险，它的桅杆差一点就撞上了桥梁。

name: The Mysterious Hostess
description: A mistress who can't see her true face is hidden behind the gauze curtain of a sedan chair. People on the street have no chance to see her beauty, but she can quietly observe the entire bustling Bianjing.

chinese.name: 神秘女主人
chinese.description: 一位不能得见真容的女主人，隐藏在轿子的纱帘后面，街上的人无缘得见她的美貌，但她可以悄悄地观察整个繁华的汴京。

name: Ship Passenger B
description: The ship is about to arrive at the pier, and the guests sitting in the cabin are looking out from the window, preparing to end this pleasant journey. At that time, there were no mobile phones or cameras or the like. Otherwise, they would have taken two photos. The photo is a souvenir.

chinese.name: 船客乙
chinese.description: 船就要抵达码头了，客舱内坐着的客人们纷纷凭窗眺望，准备结束这段愉快的旅程，那个时候还没有手机或者照相机之类的东西，不然的话，她们应该也会拍下两张照片做个纪念吧。

name: The Boatman-In-Command
description: Seeing that the mast of the passenger ship was about to crash into Hongqiao, the shipmen increased firepower to rescue them. Some shouted to the front to call the police, some loosened the rope and lowered the mast, and some struggled to use a long pole against the beam of Hongqiao. The two bows were cautious. Adjust the direction of the ship's bow accordingly, for fear of the expensive hull crashing into the river bank or other ships.

chinese.name: 指挥船工
chinese.description: 眼看客船桅杆就要撞向虹桥，船工们纷纷加开火力抢救，有的大喊向前面报警，有的松开纤绳放下桅杆，有的拼力用长杆顶住虹桥横梁，船头两位小心翼翼地调整船头方向，生怕昂贵的船身撞上河岸或者其他的船只。

name: The Shading Scholar
description: If you are afraid of going out, you don’t have to worry about it. The round fan covers your face to relieve your sorrow. Don’t be afraid to see acquaintances. In any case, this customary rule seems to have rescued the social phobia player who does not want to greet people on the street, but they are already so close, did the face-blocking action come a little later?

chinese.name: 遮面文人
chinese.description: 社恐出门不用愁，圆扇遮面来解忧，见到熟人不必怕，举起物件挡一下。不管怎样，这种约定俗成的规则似乎确实解救了这位不愿在街上和人打招呼的社交恐惧症选手，只是都已经离得这样近了，挡脸的动作是不是来得稍晚了一些？

name: The Paraffin Oil Buyer
description:
A pedestrian with a longer lamp in his hand seems to be looking for something.
"Why can't even a hawker selling lamp oil be found in this market? It's just some liquor transporters. Can they still light up the lights at night with liquor?"

chinese.name: 买油行人
chinese.description:
一位手里拿着较长灯具的行人，似乎正在四处寻觅什么。
“这街市上怎么连个卖灯油的小贩都找不到？净是些运酒的，难道他们晚上还能拿酒点灯吗？”

name: The Fortune-Telling Customer
description: On the street between the hotel and the teahouse, a man is pulling a fortune teller. He may want to find out what happened. When you feel confused about your fate, you might as well listen to these old fortune tellers.

chinese.name: 算命人
chinese.description: 酒店与茶馆的街道间，一个汉子正拉着算命先生，可能想找他测算什么事，当自己对命运感到迷茫的时候，不妨去听一下这些算命老先生的指点吧。

name: Water Carrier A
description: A water carrier who is slowly lifting a bucket placed in a well. He and the water picker next to him seem to have formed a very reasonable water picking process, from picking water to delivering water.

chinese.name: 挑水者甲
chinese.description: 一位正将置于井中的桶慢慢上提的挑水者。他和旁边的挑水者似乎共同组成了个十分合理的挑水流程，从打水到送水一条龙服务。

name: The Traveling Scholar
description: A scribe in white, wearing a mat hat, riding a tall horse, is bidding farewell to his host. You can't see the monarch when you turn around in the mountains, and you don't know when, where, and what circumstances you can meet again.

chinese.name: 远行文士
chinese.description: 一位头戴着席帽，骑着高头大马而正和下榻的主人家告别的白衣文士。山回路转不见君，此去一别，竟不知再能于何时何地何种境况相见了。

name: Arguing Scholar A
description:
A scholar who had a lively chat with people around him on the bridge seemed to be arguing about something.
"Zifeiyu, knowing the joy of fish? Isn't this just imitating Zhuangzi's Q&A? It's not a good job to find the chapter and take off the book bag."

chinese.name: 争论书生甲
chinese.description:
一位在桥上与身边人聊得酣畅的书生，似乎在争论些什么。
“子非鱼，安知鱼之乐？你这不就是模仿庄子的问答吗？寻章摘句掉书袋可算不得本事。”

name: Cash-In-Transit Guard A
description: The seemingly crude wooden car in the picture is actually a money-carrying truck. Two hotel guys are carrying and counting the copper coins. Holding so much money, even if it is not your own, you should be very excited. The bundles of copper coins are very heavy. , It is very hard to hold.

chinese.name: 运钞伙计甲
chinese.description: 图中这个看似简陋的木车其实是辆运钞车，两个酒店伙计正在搬运与清点铜钱，抱着这么多钱，就算不是自己的，也应该会很激动吧，成捆的铜钱非常沉重，抱着很是费劲。

name: The Bellman
description:
A watchman who was startled by the sound of the quarrel downstairs temporarily put down his work and looked downstairs to watch the excitement.
"The thoughts of the sir, we ordinary people really don't understand. During the day, we collect taxes on those coachmen as we please, and in the evening I want to call the watch on time. Although there are no culprits at night, the days are good. Let's go to sleep first. , I have to work at night."

chinese.name: 更夫
chinese.description:
一个被楼下吵架之声惊动了的更夫，暂时放下了手里的活计，探头向楼下看热闹。
“官老爷的心思，我们这些老百姓真是想不明白。白天对那些车夫随心所欲地收税，晚上又要我准时准点地打更。虽说现在夜晚也不见有贼人了，日子倒是不错。还是先睡罢，晚上还得做工。”

name: The Flower Seller
description: A flower grower is showing his own flower seedlings to customers. Guests, please don’t leave. Guests, please take a look. They are all newly cut branches. The blooming ones will bloom and the ones that have not bloomed. Buy a few and go back. The freshness is so delicious!

chinese.name: 卖花人
chinese.description: 一位正在向顾客展示自家花苗的花农。客人您别走，客人您来看一看，都是新剪下来的枝条，开花的将开花的还未开的都有，买几支回去，鲜妍得很哪！

name: Ship Passenger B
description: The ship is about to arrive at the pier, and the guests sitting in the cabin are looking out from the window, preparing to end this pleasant journey. At that time, there were no mobile phones or cameras or the like. Otherwise, they would have taken two photos. The photo is a souvenir.

chinese.name: 船客乙
chinese.description: 船就要抵达码头了，客舱内坐着的客人们纷纷凭窗眺望，准备结束这段愉快的旅程，那个时候还没有手机或者照相机之类的东西，不然的话，她们应该也会拍下两张照片做个纪念吧。

name: Bystander A
description: When the shipwreck was about to happen, the spectators at the bridge head pointed, or exclaimed, enclosing the right side guardrail of the arch bridge, and several people tried to rescue them by crossing the railings. In fact, in this case, everyone is the same. In a panic, no one can tell whether they are helping or adding chaos.

chinese.name: 看客甲
chinese.description: 船难将发之时，桥头的看客或指指点点，或惊呼不已，把拱桥的右侧护栏围得水泄不通，有几个人越过栏杆企图施救，其实，这种情况下，所有人都是慌张的，他们是在帮忙，还是在添乱，没人分得清楚。

name: The Laundering Old Woman
description: On the banks of the Bian River, a family boat arrived. An old woman dumped swill out of the boat. His jacket and crotchless pants were hanging on the canopy. The boat family maintained a hard drifting life on the water. This life was very hard, but it must continue.

chinese.name: 老妪
chinese.description: 汴河岸边，一条家船抵岸，一位老妪往船外倾倒泔水，船篷上晾晒着上衣和无裆裤，船家在水上维持着艰辛的漂泊生活，这样的生活很辛苦，但总得继续下去。

name: Bystander A
description: When the shipwreck was about to happen, the spectators at the bridge head pointed, or exclaimed, enclosing the right side guardrail of the arch bridge, and several people tried to rescue them by crossing the railings. In fact, in this case, everyone is the same. In a panic, no one can tell whether they are helping or adding chaos.

chinese.name: 看客甲
chinese.description: 船难将发之时，桥头的看客或指指点点，或惊呼不已，把拱桥的右侧护栏围得水泄不通，有几个人越过栏杆企图施救，其实，这种情况下，所有人都是慌张的，他们是在帮忙，还是在添乱，没人分得清楚。

name: The Palanquin-Carrier
description: A bearer who has just put down a heavy sedan chair, no matter how comfortable the people in the sedan chair are, this kind of action tool still needs manpower to carry.

chinese.name: 轿夫
chinese.description: 一位刚刚把沉重的轿子放下来的轿夫，不管在轿子里的人有多么安逸，这种行动工具终究还是需要人力来背负的。

name: The Inviting Scholar
description: A scribe respectfully invited the mistress to go out of the sedan chair to see the scenery. The posture is beautiful and polite, judging from the dressing of the crowd, the mistress in the sedan must also be of extraordinary origin.

chinese.name: 文士
chinese.description: 一位恭请女主人出轿看风景的文士。姿势端丽，形容有礼，从这一众人的穿着打扮来看，轿子里的女主人也必定出身不凡。

name: Warning Boatman A
description: Seeing that the big ship is in distress, the boatmen standing on the tops of the boats moored on both sides of the canal are giving out loud warnings, in case the bow or stern of the passenger ship will accidentally collide when adjusting the direction. If two ships of this kind of draught collide Together, the consequences will be disastrous.

chinese.name: 示警船工甲
chinese.description: 眼看大船遇险，运河两岸停泊的船顶上都站着船工在大声发出警示，以防这艘客船的船头或船尾在调整方向时会意外撞上来，这这种吃水量的两艘船一旦撞在一起，后果将不堪设想。

name: Wine-Carrying Solider B
description:
A liquor transporter who had already drunk so much that he could not figure out what he was thinking, raising his head.
"Where am I? Tokyo? No wonder this house is turning east. Who is Xiao Zhao? Me? What am I doing? Give wine to the emperor? Who is the emperor? Oh, his surname is Zhao? Why didn't he give me wine? Uh, I feel like vomiting..."

chinese.name: 运酒军卒乙
chinese.description:
一个已经喝得魂飞天外的运酒军卒，抬着头不知在想些什么。
“我是在哪啊？东京？怪不得这屋子都在往东转。小赵又是谁？我？那我在干什么？给天子送酒？天子是谁啊？哦，他也姓赵啊？那为什么不是他给我送酒呢？呃，我有点想吐……”

traits.value: Light green color matching short sleeves

name: The Cordage Stall Owner
description: This is a rope stall. Like the shoe stalls and ironware stalls around it, the stalls are placed on the side of Hongqiao. Hongqiao is already narrow. Passers-by have to walk on the crowded bridge. The vendors are quietly doing business by the side. Today, they have been driven down by the city administrators.

chinese.name: 绳摊摊主
chinese.description: 这家是个绳索摊，和周边的鞋摊、铁器摊一样都把摊摆在虹桥一侧，虹桥本就狭窄，路人不得不在拥挤的桥上穿行，小贩们却安然地在旁做生意，要是放在今天，他们早就被城管们赶下去了。

name: The Treating Teenager
description:
A teenager who was pulled by his family to seek medical advice was attracted by the accident on the street and was quietly looking back.
"It's really weird, my lord, what's so good about that wine? After drinking it, I'm drunk and unreasonable. Now I'm going crazy before drinking it. Could it be that I will get drunk when I smell it?"

chinese.name: 就医少年
chinese.description:
一个被家里人拉来寻医问诊的少年被街上的事故吸引了视线，正在悄悄地回头围观。
“大人可真怪，那酒有什么好喝的？喝了以后醉醺醺地不讲道理。现在还没喝上就已经像在发酒疯了。莫不是闻到酒味都会醉？”

name: Restaurant Guest C
description:
Business in this tea shop is booming, and the shop assistants are busy cleaning up. There is an endless stream of people who come to eat here, and a few guests are waiting for their refreshments to be served.
"Oh, I discovered the deliciousness of this store first, but now many arty people have come."

chinese.name: 食客丙
chinese.description:
这家茶肆生意正旺，店铺伙计正忙着收拾，来此处就餐的人络绎不绝，几个客人正在等待着他们的茶点端上来。
“呵，这家店的美味明明是我先发现的，现在却来了不少附庸风雅之徒。”

name: Carter B
description: The truck cover is a large-character screen written by the deposed old party. Inside the truck are collections of works and books by Sansu, Qin Guan, and Huang Tingjian. The truckmen were ordered by their owners to push them to the suburbs and burn them. If they were literate, would they? Choose to hide some of these precious books?

chinese.name: 车夫乙
chinese.description: 货车盖布是废黜旧党书写的大字屏风，车内装着的是三苏、秦观、黄庭坚的文集、书籍，车夫们奉主人之命将推其去郊外焚毁，要是他们识字的话，会不会选择把这些珍贵的书籍藏起来一些呢？

name: The Restaurant Waiter
description:
A man carrying tea utensils is preparing to add tea to the guests.
"The old customer in the middle drank too much again, so many of his friends are reliable. Ask me to quickly send this tea to the hangover, or I will get drunk in a while, I am afraid it will ruin the good things of other masters."

chinese.name: 店内伙计
chinese.description:
一位端着茶水用具的伙计，正准备给客人添茶。
“里间那位老主顾又喝多了，多得他朋友靠谱。托我赶紧把这茶水送去解解酒，不然一会发起酒疯来，怕是坏了其他老爷的好事。”

name: The Laundering Old Woman
description: On the banks of the Bian River, a family boat arrived. An old woman dumped swill out of the boat. His jacket and crotchless pants were hanging on the canopy. The boat family maintained a hard drifting life on the water. This life was very hard, but it must continue.

chinese.name: 老妪
chinese.description: 汴河岸边，一条家船抵岸，一位老妪往船外倾倒泔水，船篷上晾晒着上衣和无裆裤，船家在水上维持着艰辛的漂泊生活，这样的生活很辛苦，但总得继续下去。

name: The Refuged Porter
description: A refugee who can only be a porter, he didn't find a job all morning, so he can only stand stupidly in front of the rudimentary tea house. He stands at the door of the tea shed and wants to enter the shop and drink a bowl of tea to quench his thirst, but he doesn't know where to put the coins? He stripped off his clothes and didn't find a penny of tea money.

chinese.name: 流民挑夫
chinese.description: 只能做挑夫的流民，他一上午都没有找到活干，以至于现在只能在简陋的茶馆前傻站着，他站在茶棚门口想进店喝碗茶解渴，可是不知铜钱放在哪？他脱光衣服也没找到一文茶钱。

name: The Flower Seller
description: A flower grower is showing his own flower seedlings to customers. Guests, please don’t leave. Guests, please take a look. They are all newly cut branches. The blooming ones will bloom and the ones that have not bloomed. Buy a few and go back. The freshness is so delicious!

chinese.name: 卖花人
chinese.description: 一位正在向顾客展示自家花苗的花农。客人您别走，客人您来看一看，都是新剪下来的枝条，开花的将开花的还未开的都有，买几支回去，鲜妍得很哪！

name: The Discontent Bystander
description:
Xu is the old man who praised his ointment as a magical medicine, and there was a circle of people standing around, all of them listened carefully, and even the porter on the road looked distractedly.
"If this plaster is so amazing, it would be a good thing to buy one and go back to my father."

chinese.name: 不忿看客
chinese.description:
许是这位老者把自己的药膏夸为神药，周围站了一圈人，个个听得认真，连赶路的挑夫都分神往这边张望。
“若是这膏药真有如此神妙，买一帖回去给家父也是好事。”

name: The Begging Monk
description:
A monk with a kind smile on the street for alms. At this time of Ching Ming Festival, monks can also walk around from the temple.
"Amitabha Buddha, the benefactor is willing to give good, and he does not forget to visit privately when he is an official, and he understands the sentiments of the people. He is truly an upright official."

chinese.name: 化缘僧人
chinese.description:
一位带着和善笑容，正在当街化缘的僧人。清明节这个时候，僧人也可以从寺内出来四处走走。
“阿弥陀佛，施主乐善好施，为官而不忘微服私访，体察民情， 真乃清官也。”

name: The Luggage-Carrying Coachman
description: A horseman, carrying a bag of luggage, is chasing a runaway horse. Whether it is a horse or this bag of luggage, they are all existences that he cannot afford to lose. In other words, no matter what they are, they are much more valuable than him.

chinese.name: 拿着行李的马夫
chinese.description: 一个马夫，背着一包行李，正在追赶一匹脱缰的马。无论是马还是这包行李，都是他丢不得的存在，换句话说，无论那样的东西，都比他这人本身要有价值得多。

name: The Audience with A Child
description:
A male customer holding a baby with a mouth was attracted by the storyteller, and refused to leave even if the child on his shoulders put a lot of burden on his shoulders.
"If it weren't for this kid, I would definitely find a better place to listen to Mr.'s book."

chinese.name: 带娃听众
chinese.description:
一位抱娃带口的男性顾客，被说书人吸引住，即使肩上的孩子对他肩膀造成了不小的负担也不肯离去。
“要不是顾着这小子，我肯定能找个更好的位置听先生这段书了。”

name: The Vegetable Farmer
description:
A vegetable farmer who is selling his own vegetables to customers is eloquent and eloquent.
"Coriander, spicy green peppers, green onions, baby celery, lentils, eggplants, cucumbers, winter melons, large sea stalks, radishes, carrots, flat radishes, sprouts of toon, garlic, good leeks! Lord, you want What can I do?"

chinese.name: 菜农
chinese.description:
一位正在向客人售卖自家菜的菜农，口若悬河，滔滔不绝。
“香菜、辣青椒、勾葱、嫩芹菜、扁豆、茄子、黄瓜、架冬瓜、卖大海茄、卖萝卜、胡萝卜、扁萝卜、嫩芽的香椿、蒜儿来、好韭菜！这位爷您要来点什么？”

name: The Pole-Carrying Servant
description: A servant, a little short, had been carrying a pole behind the lord's horse a long time ago. The thing picked on the pole is usually not too heavy, that is, it contains some cooking points that can be divided among several people.

chinese.name: 挑担仆人
chinese.description: 一个仆从，有些矮小，在很久以前就跟在老爷的马屁股后面挑扁担了。扁担上挑的东西通常不会太沉，也就是装着一些能够让数人分食的炊点而已。

name: The Audience with A Child
description:
A male customer holding a baby with a mouth was attracted by the storyteller, and refused to leave even if the child on his shoulders put a lot of burden on his shoulders.
"If it weren't for this kid, I would definitely find a better place to listen to Mr.'s book."

chinese.name: 带娃听众
chinese.description:
一位抱娃带口的男性顾客，被说书人吸引住，即使肩上的孩子对他肩膀造成了不小的负担也不肯离去。
“要不是顾着这小子，我肯定能找个更好的位置听先生这段书了。”

traits.value: Light blue color matching short sleeves

name: Farmer A
description: Farmers who are going to fetch water have a well far away from the field, so they need to fill the reservoir before the dry season arrives. Using poles and buckets to carry back and forth again and again is very inefficient, but this degree of farmland reconstruction has reduced a lot of burden.

chinese.name: 农夫甲
chinese.description: 正要去挑水的农夫，水井离田地有些远，所以他们需要在旱季到来之前将蓄水池灌满。用扁担与水桶一次次的来回挑送效率很低，但这种程度的农田改造已经减轻不少负担了。

traits.value: Light blue color matching short sleeves

name: Boatman B
description: The cruise ship is about to dock. The gunmen standing on the bow and the boatmen on the top of the boat are watching the right bank closely to prevent accidents. The accidents here mainly refer to the movement of the surrounding ships, and the direction and speed of the river. .

chinese.name: 船员乙
chinese.description: 游船即将靠岸，站在船头上的篙夫、船顶上的船夫们正密切注视着右岸，以防意外发生，这里的意外主要指的是周围的船只动向，已经河水的流动方向与速度。

name: The Wood-Milling Carpenter
description:
A carpenter is polishing wood with a tool like a plane. This is a very tiring and delicate work.
"Master, this polishing is not easy, and you have to make sure that your strength can't break it."

chinese.name: 打磨木匠
chinese.description:
一个木匠，正在用像刨子之类的工具打磨木料，这是一个非常累人的精细活。
“师父，这打磨也太不容易了，又要使力气又不能坏了它。”

name: Cash-In-Transit Guard B
description: The seemingly crude wooden car in the picture is actually a money-carrying truck. Two hotel guys are carrying and counting the copper coins. Holding so much money, even if it is not your own, you should be very excited. The bundles of copper coins are very heavy. , It is very hard to hold.

chinese.name: 运钞伙计乙
chinese.description: 图中这个看似简陋的木车其实是辆运钞车，两个酒店伙计正在搬运与清点铜钱，抱着这么多钱，就算不是自己的，也应该会很激动吧，成捆的铜钱非常沉重，抱着很是费劲。

name: The Buyer
description:
A pedestrian with a delicate object in his hand seems to have just patronized the trader's business.
"Hey, don't tell me, this old man really has some strange things, and I don't know where he got it from."

chinese.name: 买货行人
chinese.description:
一位手里拿着精巧物件的行人，似是刚光顾过货郎的生意。
“嗨，你还别说，这老头还真有些稀奇玩意，也不知道他是从哪里淘来的。”

name: The Flower-Buying Hostess
description:
A traveling hostess who was originally negotiating the purchase price with the stall owner, and was attracting the attention of her own children.
"Shopkeeper, how do you sell this flower branch? Oh, you can really talk, why don't I buy more, you sell it cheaper? Hey, Xiaoyu, it's okay to hug the young master, but don't fall."

chinese.name: 买花女主人
chinese.description:
一位本来是和摊主商定着买花价钱，又正被自家幼儿吸引了注意力的出游女主人。
“店家，你这花枝如何售卖？呵，可真会说话，不如我多买些，你便宜着卖点？哎，小玉，好生抱住少爷，可不要摔着了。”

name: The Old Donkey-Riding Man
description: The old man shrank in the bitter cold, because he was old, he rode on a donkey. It may be because of the high morals, or it may be just because of the unfavorable legs and feet. In short, he is qualified to ride a donkey among a group of bipedal people.

chinese.name: 骑在驴上的老叟
chinese.description: 在苦寒中瑟缩而行的老叟，因为年迈，所以骑在驴上。有可能是因为德高望重的缘故，也有可能仅仅只是因为腿脚不利索，总之，他有资格在一群双足行走的人之中骑驴代步。

name: The Lamb Stall Owner
description:
A mutton stall owner who is wielding a knife to chop meat, but unfortunately his stall is not cared about, perhaps because the price is too expensive.
"The bearded guy is telling the story here, no one will sell meat anymore. Go, I won't cut the price, it's the storyteller's fault."

chinese.name: 羊肉摊主
chinese.description:
一位正在挥刀砍肉的羊肉摊主，但可惜他的摊位无人问津，或许是价格过于昂贵。
“大胡子这厮在这儿说书，都没人来卖肉了。去去去，我是不会降价的，都是这说书人的错。”

name: The Teenage Farmer
description: The young man who was not in his hair-cutting year led the donkey team composed of five donkeys and came to the prosperous Bianjing full of charcoal. Maybe it was for life or to sell in the city.

chinese.name: 少年农夫
chinese.description: 不及束发之年的少年，在由五只驴组成的驴队之前牵头，驼着满满当当的木炭走向繁华的汴京，也许是生活之用，也许为了到城里售卖。

name: The Child-Holding Woman
description: A woman who is walking with her child on the street may be waiting for her family, or just holding her child out to see the scenery, so that he can also feel this leisurely and prosperous Bianjing.

chinese.name: 带娃妇人
